This section contains information about integrating NNMi with directory service for consolidating the storage of user names, passwords, and optionally NNMi user group assignments.<h2>NNMi user access information and configuration options</h2><div>Together, the following items define an NNMi user:</div><div><ul><li>The user name uniquely identifies the NNMi user.</li><li>The password is associated with the NNMi user.</li><li>NNMi user group membership controls the information available and the type of actions the user can take in the NNMi console.</li></ul></div>